We know there are many out there and pretty good. But we are bringing our flavor to it and adding a little bit of spice too.
We took the Mrg release and took out the universal bit of it since it looked like it was added from some other film. Then
we went looking for the infamous plane bit and took the one from the trailer and added to the begining of our video.
Is it the whole bit we dont know as we havent been out to see it yet but what ever we found we used it. Then it was
on to subbing the non english parts so that our non Spanish speaking brothers can understand a bit better what's
going on. We will advise they might be out by a milisecond or two but very close to the others. Then finally it was
to the rest of the film we did our usuall to it and tried to brighten it enough and not kill the black. A BIG THANKS
TO OUR BROTHER HIVE/CM8 FOR THIS GREAT AUDIO AND WHOMEVER WENT AND GOT IT KUDOS TO ALL. Hope you all
enjoy this release as much as we did making it for you all. Check sample as screens always look better.
